        <h1>For podcasters!</h1>
      </div>
    </header>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="copy">
	We love podcasting! After we released our first episodes by
	manually copying files to servers, making sure our MP3 metadata
	matched the episode's description, updating our RSS feed, and
	setting up the Web site for each of the episodes, we realized
	there had to be a better way. Because the major services lacked
	all of our dream features, we set out to make a great podcasting
	platform. And, it's coming soon for you to use, too.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
